      (comap_coe_neBot_of_le_principal hl) _ _ hf hg ha' (he.comap _)
  exact ‚ü®b, b.prop, h‚ü©
#align is_preconnected.intermediate_value‚ÇÇ_eventually‚ÇÅ IsPreconnected.intermediate_value‚ÇÇ_eventually‚ÇÅ

